Reviews

review by - YELP

Linda H:

Totally amazing! Complimentary chips and salsa immediately. The sheer volume of food for the $ was unbelievable......and delicious! Beef quesadilla...

review by - YELP

Andrew G:

Went here for a usual quick Mexican lunch and got pleasantly surprised by a more upscale and high quality Mexican restaurant but with the same quickness and good prices...

review by - YELP

Dorothy-Faye S:

Great food, reasonable price. Friendly staff. Excellent margaritas. Delivery through the apps was quick and no errors.

review by - YELP

Dr. Scott C:

Agaves Cantina Yezzzz finally a great Mexican Restaurant West Ashley!! Excellent Margaritas, my favorite is the Azul's Treasure, Yummy!! For appetizer get the Queso Fundido with Ground Beef soooo good...

review by - YELP

Daniela Z:

Honestly thought this was going to be basic... but it's really good! They've got great vegetarian options that don't just mean cheese, you just need to ask...
